Abosh D. ,  Rosser B. ,  Kaita K. ,  Bazylewski R. ,  Minuk G. :  Outcomes following liver transplantation for patients with alcohol- versus nonalcoholic-induced liver diasease.  Can J Gastroenterol ,  2000 ;  14 :  851
